        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e948bb03-ddd3-404a-a220-ba5536573153">
                Mr. Morgan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e948bb03-ddd3-404a-a220-ba5536573153" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-01-31/debates/25c7a3f6-1061-44e6-bd29-f4b5f1c22eed/1922Committee(CabinetMinistersStatements)#contribution-e948bb03-ddd3-404a-a220-ba5536573153">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I take it from the answer that the right hon. Gentleman will be prepared to meet Members on this side of the House under conditions similar to those under which he meets Members on the other side, and on a similar status?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
